# --- 6.3 Tenant overlays (Python-only convenience; scope.md Q9 + TPRD §15.32 validation) ---
class TenantKVStore:
    """Tenant-scoped KV wrapper. Prefixes every key with f'{tenant_id}.'.
    Rejects cross-tenant reads (filters non-prefixed keys from watch_all).
    [traces-to: TPRD-§8.3-TenantKVStore]
