    (tracecontext|traceparent → W3C; baggage; b3; b3multi; jaeger).
    Default if empty/unrecognized: composite of tracecontext + baggage.
    Sets resource attrs from ServiceInfo (service.name, service.version,
    deployment.environment).
    Renamed from Go SDK's `Init` per PEP 8 (Python's exported convention is
    snake_case for module-level functions). Behavior is identical to Go's Init.
    [traces-to: TPRD-§10.1-tracer-Init]
    """
    ...

def get_tracer(name: str, version: str = "") -> Any:
    """Cached tracer per (name, version) via functools.cache. Always use this
    over global tracer with __name__ (mirrors Go SDK rule 6 quality standard).
    [traces-to: TPRD-§10-get-tracer]
    """
